::I honestly think that these discussions are "dispute resolution", ([[User talk:Justanother/Archive4#Personal_attack_on_User:Anynobody]],[[User_talk:Justanother/Archive4#/Personal attacks in edit summaries]], [[User_talk:Justanother/Archive4#Be_nice.]]) since [[User:Bishonen|Bishonen]] deemed it to not be "dispute resolution" it seemed like she was saying [[User:Smeelgova|Smeelgova]] was acting in "bad faith" based on her description of [[User:Smeelgova|Smeelgova's]] efforts. (If [[User:Smeelgova|Smeelgova]] wasn't trying to resolve anything by addressing [[User:Justanother|Justanother's]] behavior, wouldn't that be acting in bad faith?)
