*Just for chuckles, we should keep in mind that, when writing an academic paper or business presentation, the rule is 250 words is a page.  Therefore, the nomination was 20 pages.  It's probably best, if you're going past a "page," to put your arguments on a page in your user space and then say, "See ''pagename'' for arguments."  Otherwise, the long slog that is AfD becomes endless.  [[User:Geogre|Geogre]] 10:26, 12 March 2007 (UTC)
