== Indef blocked User:Pogsurf sockpuppetry ==

Hi, the [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Log&type=block&page=User:Pogsurf indef blocked] [[User:Pogsurf]] (vandalism only account) is evading their block with a sockpuppet, [[User:Lobster blogster]]. Both users demonstrated a high level of Wikipedia skill immediately after registration, and have demonstrated the same MO by editing a very narrow range of articles (especially [[Paul Staines]] and [[Claire Ward]], who is the current MP for Watford, a page Lobster blogster has also edited) and repeatedly linking to the same ''Guardian'' article. Also, a quick google confirms the link between "Pogsurf", "Lobster blogster", and Watford, however I won't post the links as it's poor wikiquette to reveal peoples' real names online unless they volunteer them. I raised this first on [[User:Majorly]]'s [[User talk:Majorly#Paul Staines|talk page]], but moving it here to go through the official channels. Could an admin deal please? Cheers, [[User:DWaterson|DWaterson]] 16:03, 5 March 2007 (UTC)

:Just to add more proof, see [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Talk:Paul_Staines&action=history], [[User:62.136.198.105]] appears to be the same as [[User:Lobster blogster]]. [[User:Pogsurf]] had an anonymous alter ego, which was [[User:62.136.238.65]]. A quick comparison of their edit histories shows this, and [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=User_talk:62.136.238.65&diff=109272579&oldid=109195908] shows Pogsurf thanking another user for a comment left on 62.136.238.65's talk page - something he'd only do if they are the same. Note that 62.136.198.105 and 62.136.238.65 are the same ISP, and both perform the same kind of edits. This shows that 62.136.238.65, 62.136.238.65, Pogsurf and Lobster Blogster are one and the same. Note as well that Lobster Blogster has also edited the Watford talk page, with a very similar comment to one Pogsurf left on articles before he was banned. And Pogsurf was often editing  Claire Ward - who is the MP for Watford. [[User:Nssdfdsfds|Nssdfdsfds]] 16:51, 5 March 2007 (UTC)



